grahanam ( english translation : the eclipse ) is a 2004 telugu film directed by indraganti mohan krishna .   the film is based on dosha gunam a story written by gudipati venkatachalam , popularly known as chalam .   the film won critical acclaim upon release and received national film award , for the best first film of a director .   the film premiered at the 2005 international film festival of india , the 2004 seattle first independent south asian film festival and the 2004 mumbai asian film festival .